    Implement Cloudinary image management integration
    
    - Replace complex server-side image handling with Cloudinary cloud service
    - Add ImageApiService for direct Cloudinary API interactions (upload/delete)
    - Update admin and technician components to use immediate upload/delete
    - Implement permission-based deletion (admin: all images, technician: own images)
    - Add image naming convention: servicecall_username_date_timestamp
    - Remove complex database image path management and physical file handling
    - Fix character encoding issues in SMS (French accents)
    - Add language preference support (default to French)
    - Update template editing for email/SMS with bilingual support
    - Sort service provider lists alphabetically
    - Add language column to client list
    - Fix notification template editing in admin calendar
    - Remove send notification button from technician page
    - Update translation labels and UI improvements

